# HoloSuite — Multi-License Overview

This repository contains multiple modules, each licensed independently.

## Tier 1: Core (LGPL-3.0-or-later)

The following modules are licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public
License v3.0 or later. You may build extensions and applications that
use these modules without your code being subject to copyleft, but
modifications to the modules themselves must be shared under the same
license.

- holosuite-core/
- shared/

See holosuite-core/LICENSE and shared/LICENSE for the full license text.

## Tier 2: Free Submodules (GPL-3.0-or-later)

The following modules are licensed under the GNU General Public License
v3.0 or later. You may use, study, and modify these modules freely, but
any distribution of modified versions must also be licensed under the GPL.

- bounty-board/
- csi-toolkit/
- galaxy-map/
- holocall/
- holosuite-critical-cutin/
- holosuite-hacking/
- security-cameras/

See any of their LICENSE files for the full license text.

## Tier 3: Premium Modules (PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0)

The following modules are source-available under the PolyForm
Noncommercial License 1.0.0. The source code is viewable, but
redistribution and commercial use are prohibited. Access is provided
through Patreon.

- pulse-scanner/

See pulse-scanner/LICENSE for the full license text.

## Asset Licenses

Some assets (such as audio files) may carry their own licenses.
Check individual directories for details.
